This paper is about deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper focuses on the trade-off between exploration and exploitation in RL, which is a common problem in the field. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
